reviewText:
This is probably the weakest three-star review that I've ever given, and it rates this highly only and I mean ONLY because of one model in this cast who gets down on her hands and knees and shows the camera everything that a heterosexual male ever would want to see. Also, for those of you who like her, Christine Nguyen makes an appearance here and she is absolutely adorable, but I've never liked her as a nude model. Her interview was more meaningful than her nudity, and it actually improved this product slightly.

As for the rest of it...most of the girls are below-average (average at best), the vast majority of the dozen have bargain-basement implant jobs and the videos are awful. I realize that these are home videos but come on...lighting atrocious, framing horrible, angles miss what you really want to see. Scenery? Well, grass that hasn't been mowed in two weeks and mildewed shower tiles. Yep, that about sums it up.

It's almost startling to see how much this series tanked after the first offering. I found myself watching a minute or so of some of the models before skipping ahead to the next. Don't buy this. Don't rent this. Don't watch this. Look for something else to do with your time and money.
